==English==

===Noun===
'''earwig'''  (''plural:'' '''[[earwigs]]''')
# A type of crawling insect, that after getting inside fruit that is sitting on the ground, will become a [[June bug]].

====Scientific names====
*order [[Dermaptera]]<!-- the entire order -->
*[[Forficula auricularia]] (''common earwig'')

